{"items":[{"title":"ALLBUS - General Social Surveys 1970-1990","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/44965","justification":"The ALLBUS series contains repeated cross-sectional surveys, many of which cover political attitudes and behaviour in West Germany, and run from 1970 onward.  It is a core dataset for this research area, and GESIS is the primary host and DOI provider."},{"title":"German Longitudinal Election Study (GLES) 1972-1980","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/45572","justification":"This longitudinal study specifically focuses on electoral behaviour and political attitudes, covering the 1970s and is hosted by GESIS. Includes pre- and post-election surveys."},{"title":"Political Attitudes in West Germany 1972-1980","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/45614","justification":"A dataset specifically addressing political attitudes, this covers the period 1972-1980, making it highly relevant and hosted by GESIS."}, {"title":"Microdata of the German Political Elite – 1972","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/46001","justification":"Though focused on the elite, this provides context for political behaviour during that period and is a GESIS hosted dataset."}, {"title":"Infratest/GESIS Datenarchiv - Data on German elections 1949-1994","url_or_doi":"https://www.gesis.org/en/services/data-access/data-archives/infratest-gesis-datenarchiv","justification":"This archive contains numerous datasets related to German elections, many of which fall within the 1970s and provide insights into political behaviour. It is a landing page for the archive."}, {"title":"Values of the German Population 1980-1990","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/44955","justification":"While starting at the end of the 70s and extending into the 80s, this dataset provides relevant data on values and their influence on political attitudes. Hosted by GESIS."}, {"title":"Political Action - Data from the 1970s","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/45568","justification":"Specifically named for the 1970s and focusing on political action, this is a relevant dataset, hosted by GESIS."}, {"title":"Documentation: ALLBUS - General Social Surveys 1970-1990","url_or_doi":"https://www.gesis.org/en/services/data-access/data-archives/allbus/allbus-1970-1990","justification":"Landing page for the full ALLBUS archive, provides access and details to many relevant surveys from the 1970s."}, {"title":"Materialien zur Analyse von Wahlforschung (MAW)","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/45949","justification":"Dataset offering materials for analysing election research. Contains data points potentially relevant to the 1970s and hosted by GESIS."}, {"title":"Politische Einstellungen in Deutschland 1976-1986","url_or_doi":"https://doi.org/10.48488/45613","justification":"Directly addresses political attitudes in Germany, spanning a significant portion of the 1970s. GESIS hosted DOI."}]}
